      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken has browned, add your <strong>dried</strong> <strong>thyme</strong> and <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> <strong>paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>creamy stock</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil</p><p>Season with a very generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until thickened</p>",
      "order": 5,
