      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Squeeze the pouch[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>of <strong>cooked brown long grain rice</strong> to separate the grains</p><p>Tear the top corner of the pouch[es]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>(just a little!) and <strong>microwave</strong> for 2 min or until piping hot</p><p>Tip: If you're cooking two pouches, pop them in together but increase the microwave cook time accordingly</p>",
