    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, add the<strong> drained lentils</strong> and <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 1-2 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>French-style mustard & garlic chicken</strong></p>",
